the rename works fine.

So it seams to be a something with my project...
But of course I have no idea what that could be...

So, it looks like problem does not come from JDT/Core component.
Looking at stack trace, it seems that this NPE is due to the fact that provided
IJavaElement was null which is an invalid contract for this API method.
Move to JDT/UI for comments/ideas on how this could happen or move to Platform...

Was indeed a problem in JDT/UI.
